data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained residence, where charm meets contemporary elegance. The updated kitchen steals the show with a large quartz island and custom cabinets, seamlessly flowing into the cozy family room with a fireplace. Outside, a large yard on corner lot enclosed by a stylish vinyl fence offers privacy for outdoor enjoyment. A large stamped concrete patio is perfect for al fresco entertaining. Inside, new modern interior paint and carpet enhance the ambiance. Four bedrooms include a luxurious primary suite with an en suite bathroom and walk-in closet. With updated exterior paint, this home exudes curb appeal.  Basement has egress window and plumbed for 3/4 bath ready for your finishing touch. Quick possession available. Don't miss your chance to call this dream home yours – schedule a showing today! Pre-Inspected
